song_name: This Is Why We Cant Be Friends

version_description: In this acoustic version released June 2018, Niall plays his palm-muted strum differently from the studio version, and he plays an F#m11 chord instead of F#m. The tempo is about 4 beats per minute faster than on the album, giving this version a more dynamic and powerful groove. You can listen and watch it here https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=cKbl19xeSIQ.
Includes chords and main guitar/keyboard leads.
These are the chords to the music video here: https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=zC30BYR3CUk.
